snippet.title: Arcade Archives NEOGEO: The King of Fighters '94 - PlayStation 4 Gameplay
snippet.description:
This is a re-release of the NEOGEO version of The King of Fighters '94. This video is made in honor of the series' 30th anniversary, as this was the game that started it all.

Arcade Archives (C) Hamster Corporation
NEOGEO, The King of Fighters, The King of Fighters '94 (C) SNK
Arcade Archives NEOGEO Version also released on Nintendo Switch, Xbox One and Windows 10
